        🛒 Buy Basic Kit (€49)
      </a>
      <a href="https://smbcyberhub.gumroad.com/l/prokit" class="bg-white border border-emerald-600 text-emerald-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50">
        ✅ Get Pro Kit (€99)
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-8 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm text-left text-gray-800 border border-gray-300 divide-x divide-gray-300">
