  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-10 px-6 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
    <div class="border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm bg-white">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Free Sample</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1 mb-2">
        <li>Preview training slide and checklist</li>
        <li>No registration or tracking</li>
        <li>Great for quick demos</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Perfect if you want to see real kit content before buying. Not enough for full compliance but a fast way to evaluate.</p>
    </div>
