        <li>All core modules for small teams</li>
        <li>Printable PDFs, 1-team license</li>
        <li>Quick deployment for simple compliance</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Choose if you want affordable, essential training and checklists for a single team, without extra features or complexity.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm bg-white">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Pro Kit</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1 mb-2">
        <li>All Basic features plus advanced modules</li>
        <li>Extra quizzes, onboarding guides, unlimited use</li>
        <li>Full GDPR/ISO audit toolkit</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Best for companies prepping for audits, insurance, or wanting a comprehensive, print-ready security training solution.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10 px-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">FAQs</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-left">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Is the Free Sample Kit enough for compliance?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">The Free Sample Kit is a preview to help you evaluate the content and delivery style. It is not intended to fulfill full GDPR or audit requirements, but gives you a real module, checklist, and quiz from the Pro Kit.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Do I need to create an account or use any software?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">No logins, SaaS, or software are required. All kits are delivered as printable PDFs and documents for maximum privacy and offline delivery.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">How is the Pro Kit different from the Basic Kit?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">The Pro Kit includes all Basic Kit materials plus advanced modules (multi-factor authentication, social engineering, ransomware), onboarding guides, extra checklists, and unlimited internal use for larger teams.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Can I upgrade later if I start with the Free or Basic Kit?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, you can try the Free Sample at any time and upgrade to Basic or Pro as your needs grow. No subscriptions or recurring fees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
